# ChangeLog for sys-kernel/clip-kernel

*clip-kernel-4.9.74-r1 (10 Jul 2018)

  10 Jul 2018; Mickaël Salaün <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-4.9.74-r1.ebuild, -clip-kernel-4.9.74.ebuild:
  Patches cleanup.

*clip-kernel-4.4.135 (06 Jun 2018)

  06 Jun 2018; Thibaut Sautereau <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-4.4.135.ebuild, -clip-kernel-4.4.127-r2.ebuild:
  Update to 4.4.135.

*clip-kernel-4.4.127-r2 (09 May 2018)

  09 May 2018; Thibaut Sautereau <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-4.4.127-r2.ebuild, -clip-kernel-4.4.127-r1.ebuild:
  Fix broken O_MAYEXEC support due to upstream change.

*clip-kernel-4.4.127-r1 (09 May 2018)

  09 May 2018; Thibaut Sautereau <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-4.4.127-r1.ebuild, -clip-kernel-4.4.127.ebuild:
  Unset CONFIG_CLSM_CHROOT_PTRACE when debugging so we can use strace.

*clip-kernel-4.4.127 (17 Apr 2018)

  17 Apr 2018; Thibaut Sautereau <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-4.4.127.ebuild, -clip-kernel-4.4.113-r1.ebuild:
  Update to 4.4.127.

*clip-kernel-4.4.113-r1 (07 Feb 2018)

  07 Feb 2018; Timothée Ravier <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-4.4.113-r1.ebuild, -clip-kernel-4.4.113.ebuild:
  Update 4.4 kernel config.

*clip-kernel-4.9.74 (07 Feb 2018)

  07 Feb 2018; Timothée Ravier <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-4.9.74.ebuild, -clip-kernel-4.9.58.ebuild:
  Update to 4.9.74. Update kernel config.

*clip-kernel-4.4.113 (29 Jan 2018)

  29 Jan 2018; Timothée Ravier <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-4.4.113.ebuild, -clip-kernel-4.4.109.ebuild:
  Update to 4.4.113. Update kernel config.

*clip-kernel-4.4.109 (24 Jan 2018)

  24 Jan 2018; Timothée Ravier <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-4.4.109.ebuild, -clip-kernel-4.4.49-r4.ebuild:
  Update to 4.4.109. Update kernel config.

*clip-kernel-4.4.49-r3.ebuild (23 Nov 2017)

  23 Nov 2017; Tony Cheneau <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  files/initrd-clip,
  +clip-kernel-4.4.49-r4.ebuild, -clip-kernel-4.4.49-r3.ebuild:
  Fix for the init script, where the user would input a wrong
  password at first, when setting or changing its current encryption
  password. The bug would cause the input to be prefixed by the
  previous password attempts, and would encrypt the system with a
  password the user could not know.

*clip-kernel-3.14.79-r11 (25 Aug 2017)

  25 Aug 2017; Nicolas Godinho <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-3.14.79-r11.ebuild, -clip-kernel-3.14.79-r10.ebuild:
  Increase CONFIG_BLK_DEV_RAM_SIZE (i.e. maximum size for ramdisks) to 128 MiB
  in order for the CLIP installer LiveCD kernel to be able to properly create
  the initrd ramdisk. The reason behind this is the initrd image which can be
  quite big since it contains a lot of (more-or-less useful) modules.

*clip-kernel-4.4.49-r3 clip-kernel-3.14.79-r10 (03 Jul 2017)

  03 Jul 2017; Nicolas Belouin <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  files/initrd-clip,
  +clip-kernel-4.4.49-r3.ebuild, -clip-kernel-4.4.49-r2.ebuild:
  Fix some issue with full disk encryption migration.


  17 May 2017; Nicolas Belouin <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +config-4.4.livecd, +nfs_livecd.patch, clip-kernel-4.4.49-r2.ebuild:
  Add livecd configuration and a small patch for nfs support.

  16 May 2017; Tony Cheneau <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  files/config-3.14.livecd:
  Provide new configuration for the kernel (latest update added
  GCC_PLUGINS and DEBUG_RODATA)

*clip-kernel-4.4.49-r2 (10 May 2017)

  10 May 2017; Tony Cheneau <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-4.4.49-r2.ebuild, -clip-kernel-4.4.49-r1.ebuild,
  config-4.4.modular-smp:
  Enable MAC_80211_RC_MINSTREL. This is required for the ath9k driver (Wifi) to
  work correctly. ath9k is the default driver for the Wifi card of the Toshiba
  R830.

*clip-kernel-3.14.79-r9 (20 Apr 2017)

  20 Apr 2017; Timothée Ravier <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-3.14.79-r9.ebuild, -clip-kernel-3.14.79-r8.ebuild:
  RBump to fix randomize_va_space value.

*clip-kernel-4.4.49-r1 (19 Apr 2017)

  19 Apr 2017; Timothée Ravier <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-4.4.49-r1.ebuild, -clip-kernel-4.4.49.ebuild:
  RBump to fix randomize_va_space value + minor fix in patches.

*clip-kernel-3.14.79-r8 (24 Feb 2017)

  24 Feb 2017; Timothée Ravier <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-3.14.79-r8.ebuild, -clip-kernel-3.14.79-r7.ebuild:
  Update to grsecurity-3.1-3.14.79-201702022041.

*clip-kernel-4.4.49 (20 Feb 2017)

  20 Feb 2017; Timothée Ravier <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-4.4.49.ebuild, -clip-kernel-4.4.45-r1.ebuild:
  Update to 4.4.49 kernel, grsecurity-3.1-4.4.49-201702152050.

*clip-kernel-3.14.79-r7 (17 Feb 2017)

  17 Feb 2017; Thomas Letan <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-3.14.79-r7.ebuild, -clip-kernel-3.14.79-r6.ebuild:
  Enable CLIP-TPM support within the CLIP kernel.

*clip-kernel-3.14.79-r6 (08 Feb 2017)

  08 Feb 2017; Timothée Ravier <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-3.14.79-r6.ebuild, -clip-kernel-3.14.79-r5.ebuild:
  Import updated PF_RING patches.

*clip-kernel-3.14.79-r5 (02 Feb 2017)

  02 Feb 2017; Timothée Ravier <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-3.14.79-r5.ebuild, -clip-kernel-3.14.79-r4.ebuild:
  Fix strict TPE logging (clip-patches).

*clip-kernel-4.4.13-r4 (11 Jan 2017)

  11 Jan 2017; Nicolas Belouin <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-4.4.13-r4.ebuild, -clip-kernel-4.4.13-r3.ebuild:
  Add a "*" to accept 4.4.x packages for firmwares

*clip-kernel-3.14.79-r4 (21 Dec 2016)

  21 Dec 2016; Thomas Letan <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-3.14.79-r4.ebuild, -clip-kernel-3.14.79-r3.ebuild:
  Add tpm support for clip-livecd

*clip-kernel-4.4.13-r3 clip-kernel-3.14.79 (28 Nov 2016)

  28 Nov 2016; Nicolas Belouin <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-4.4.13-r3.ebuild, -clip-kernel-4.4.13-r2.ebuild,
  +clip-kernel-3.14.79-r3.ebuild, -clip-kernel-3.14.79.ebuild,
  files/mkinitrd.clip-3.13, files/mkinitrd.clip-3.13:
  Add rm symlink to busybox in initrd -fix issue with full encryption migration.
  Also bump clip-kernel one more time to ensure upgrade from clip-4.4.2

*clip-kernel-4.4.13-r2 (23 Nov 2016)

  23 Nov 2016; Yves-Alexis Perez <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-4.4.13-r2.ebuild, -clip-kernel-4.4.13-r1.ebuild:
  files/config-4.4.modular-smp:
  Re-enable CONFIG_USB_NET_DRIVERS on i386.

  10 Nov 2016; Yves-Alexis Perez <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  files/config-3.14.livecd:
  Explicit disable of hibernation.

*clip-kernel-3.14.79 (20 Oct 2016)

  20 Oct 2016; Timothée Ravier <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-3.14.79.ebuild, -clip-kernel-3.14.73-r3.ebuild:
  Linux 3.14.79 & grsecurity-3.1-3.14.79-201610200106 update to fix
  CVE-2016-5195.

*clip-kernel-3.14.73-r3 (19 Oct 2016)

  19 Oct 2016; Alain Ozanne <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-3.14.73-r3.ebuild, -clip-kernel-3.14.73-r2.ebuild:
  Cgroups activation.

  12 Oct 2016; Yves-Alexis Perez <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +files/config-4.4.devstation,
  +files/config-4.4.modular-smp.amd64:
  Add config files for devstation and amd64 modular-smp.

*clip-kernel-4.4.13-r1 clip-kernel-3.14.73-r2 (04 Oct 2016)

  04 Oct 2016; Nicolas Belouin <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  files/initrd,
  +clip-kernel-3.14.73-r2.ebuild, -clip-kernel-3.14.73-r1.ebuild,
  +clip-kernel-4.4.13-r1.ebuild, -clip-kernel-4.4.13.ebuild:
  Add way to change disk encryption password.

*clip-kernel-4.4.13 (17 Aug 2016)

  17 Aug 2016; Timothée Ravier <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-4.4.13.ebuild, files/config-4.4.modular-smp:
  Add clip-kernel 4.4.13 with initial kernel config based on 3.14 config.

*clip-kernel-3.14.73-r1 (12 Jul 2016)

  12 Jul 2016; Timothée Ravier <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-3.14.73-r1.ebuild, -clip-kernel-3.14.73.ebuild:
  Fix the vserver patch ported on top of grsecurity.

*clip-kernel-3.14.73 (28 Jun 2016)

  28 Jun 2016; Yves-Alexis Perez <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-3.14.73.ebuild, -clip-kernel-3.14.68-r1.ebuild:
  Update kernel to 3.14.73, grsecurity to 3.1-3.14.73-201606280007.
  Backport fixes for trackpoint/touchpad support on 2015 Lenovo ThinkPads.

*clip-kernel-3.14.68-r1 (24 May 2016)

  24 May 2016; Timothée Ravier <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-3.14.68-r1.ebuild, -clip-kernel-3.14.68.ebuild:
  Backport GCC version check update from upstream to fix GCC plugin check in
  grsecurity patch.

*clip-kernel-3.14.68 (10 May 2016)

  10 May 2016; Timothée Ravier <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-3.14.68.ebuild, -clip-kernel-3.14.65-r1.ebuild:
  Update kernel to 3.14.68, grsecurity to 3.1-3.14.68-201605071727.

*clip-kernel-3.14.65-r1 (29 Mar 2016)

  29 Mar 2016; Tony Cheneau <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-3.14.65-r1.ebuild, -clip-kernel-3.14.65.ebuild:
  Activate AES-NI within kernel (not as a module) on all compatible platforms.

*clip-kernel-3.14.65 (18 Mar 2016)

  18 Mar 2016; Yves-Alexis Perez <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
