  Add config, based on modular-smp.amd64 and livecd.

  27 Nov 2015; Yves-Alexis Perez <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  files/config-3.14.modular-smp.amd64:
  Update config, disable CONFIG_IOSF_MBI (unneeded).

*clip-kernel-3.14.51-r2 (16 Oct 2015)

  16 Oct 2015; Tony Cheneau <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-3.14.51-r2.ebuild, -clip-kernel-3.14.51-r1.ebuild:
  Improve i915 support (add lots of patches for the Broadwell graphic stack that
  come from more recent kernels).

  12 Oct 2015; Mickaël Salaün <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  clip-kernel-3.14.51-r1.ebuild:
  Tied to the same linux-headers version, needed anyway by compilation tools.

  28 Sep 2015; Yves-Alexis Perez <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  clip-kernel-3.14.51-r1.ebuild, files/config-3.14.livecd,
  files/config-3.14.modular-smp.amd64:
  Enable rtwifi options also in modular-smpd.amd64 and clip-livecd config file,
  fix build failure.

*clip-kernel-3.14.51-r1 (14 Sep 2015)

  14 Sep 2015; Tony Cheneau <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-3.14.51-r1.ebuild, -clip-kernel-3.14.51.ebuild,
  files/config-3.14.modular-smp:
  Backport rtlwifi from 3.18 kernel

