*clip-kernel-3.14.40 (05 May 2015)

  05 May 2015; Yves-Alexis Perez <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-3.14.40.ebuild, -clip-kernel-3.14.39-r3.ebuild,
  files/config-3.14.modular-smp:
  Bump kernel to 3.14.40, grsec to 3.1-3.14.40-201505042052.
  Re-enable DOS partition support, lost with EFI changes.

*clip-kernel-3.14.39-r3 (28 Apr 2015)

  28 Apr 2015; Thomas Letan <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-3.14.39-r3.ebuild, -clip-kernel-3.14.39-r2.ebuild:
