*clip-kernel-3.14.39-r2 (28 Apr 2015)

  28 Apr 2015; Thomas Letan <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-3.14.39-r2.ebuild, -clip-kernel-3.14.39-r1.ebuild:
  Add Surface Pro Cover 3 support

*clip-kernel-3.14.39-r1 (21 Apr 2015)

  21 Apr 2015; Piotr Chmielnicki <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
