*clip-kernel-3.14.39 (20 Apr 2015)

  20 Apr 2015; Yves-Alexis Perez <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-3.14.39.ebuild, -clip-kernel-3.14.38.ebuild:
  Bump kernel to 3.14.39, grsec to 3.1-3.14.39-201504190814.

*clip-kernel-3.14.38 (15 Apr 2015)

  15 Apr 2015; Yves-Alexis Perez <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-3.14.38.ebuild, -clip-kernel-3.14.37.ebuild,
