*clip-kernel-3.2.16-r3 (22 May 2012)

  22 May 2012; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-3.2.16-r3.ebuild, -clip-kernel-3.2.16-r2.ebuild,
  files/config-3.2.2.modular-smp:
