*clip-kernel-2.6.39.4-r2 (16 Aug 2011)

  16 Aug 2011; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-2.6.39.4-r2.ebuild, -clip-kernel-2.6.39.4-r1.ebuild:
  Bump clip-patches, add upstream patches for :
   - sysfs_remove_battery race condition (#35642)
   - ALPS touchpad initialization on some DELL notepads (#14660).
   - fixes from 2.6.33.18: alsa timer NULL pointer dereference, use
   MD5 to generate protocol sequence numbers.
  Bump clip-lsm - make blocked signals messages INFO rather than WARNING.

