  - add error handling in crypt0 code.

*clip-kernel-2.6.39.4 (04 Aug 2011)

  04 Aug 2011; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-2.6.39.4.ebuild, -clip-kernel-2.6.39.3.ebuild,
  +files/postinst.modrename, -files/postinst.brcm80211:
  Bump to .4. Fix clip-lsm initialization issues. Add new 
  /etc/modules fix : snd-hda-codec-intelhdmi -> snd-hda-codec-hdmi.

*clip-kernel-2.6.39.3 (02 Aug 2011)

  02 Aug 2011; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-2.6.39.3.ebuild, -clip-kernel-2.6.38.8-r6.ebuild,
  -files/config-2.6.38.8*, +files/config-2.6.39.3.*,
  +files/postinst.brcm80211:
  Bump to 2.6.39.3. Add postinst snippet to deal with the fact 
  that brcm80211 was renamed to brcmsmac...

*clip-kernel-2.6.38.8-r6 (29 Jul 2011)

  29 Jul 2011; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-2.6.38.8-r6.ebuild, -clip-kernel-2.6.38.8-r5.ebuild,
  +files/postint.iwlwifi:
  Add a postinst snippet to add missing firmware files to /etc/firmwares
  on hardware configs using iwlagn. The iwlagn module in kernel 2.6.38 now
  requests its firmware at module init time, rather than when first accessing
  the interface from userspace - hence the firmware needs to be in the 
  initrd.
  On the other hand, postinst.vga, postinst.kms and postinst.udf are no longer
  included - these fixes should be applied everywhere by now.

*clip-kernel-2.6.38.8-r5 (29 Jul 2011)

  29 Jul 2011; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-2.6.38.8-r5.ebuild, -clip-kernel-2.6.38.8-r4.ebuild:
  Bump clip-lsm - refine AF_NETLINK checks, so that CLSM_PRIV_NETLINK
  is only required to use NETLINK sockets other than NETLINK_ROUTE, and
  to send 'write' (SET/NEW/DEL) messages on a NETLINK_ROUTE socket. 
  That way, we allow GET messages on NETLINK_ROUTE sockets without 
  specific privileges, since such messages are sent all over the place
  by pretty much any process accessing the network.

*clip-kernel-2.6.38.8-r4 (26 Jul 2011)

  26 Jul 2011; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-2.6.38.8-r4.ebuild, -clip-kernel-2.6.38.8-r3.ebuild:
  Bump clip-lsm - fix fd transmission chroot checks, fix some build
  errors with different config sets.

*clip-kernel-2.6.38.8-r3 (19 Jul 2011)

  19 Jul 2011; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-2.6.38.8-r3.ebuild, -clip-kernel-2.6.38.8-r2.ebuild:
  Bump clip-patches - fix O_MAYEXEC support.

  18 Jul 2011; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  files/config-2.6.38.livecd:
  Add ATA_PIIX and UHCI builtin drivers to livecd config, for
  use in KVM.

*clip-kernel-2.6.38.8-r2 (13 Jul 2011)

  13 Jul 2011; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-2.6.38.8-r2.ebuild, -clip-kernel-2.6.38.8-r1.ebuild:
  Bump clip-patches - force a keyboard reset on resume.

