*clip-kernel-2.6.32.42 (24 Jun 2011)

  24 Jun 2011; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-2.6.32.42.ebuild, -clip-kernel-2.6.32.41-r2.ebuild:
  Bump to latest stable.
  Bump clip-patches - minor bump to grsec patch, major bump from debian
  to drm-update patch.

  07 Jun 2011; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  clip-kernel-2.6.32.41-r2.ebuild, +files/linux-2.6.32-asm-bitsperlong.patch:
  Add a patch to fix includes for userland compilation (clip-devstation only).

