*clip-kernel-2.6.32.33-r1 (23 Mar 2011)

  23 Mar 2011; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-2.6.32.33-r1.ebuild, -clip-kernel-2.6.32.33.ebuild,
  -files/mkinird.clip.2, files/mkinitrd.clip:
  Bump clip-lsm :
   - do not allow reading kern log buffer with CAP_SYS_ADMIN
   - remove swapoff_open hooks, no longer needed since we don't
   need to unmount /dev anymore
  Initrd generation : rename new script to overwrite old. Change 
  expected path for compiled fr mapping to avoid conflicts with
  standard mappings.

*clip-kernel-2.6.32.33 (22 Mar 2011)

