*clip-kernel-2.6.29.6-r6 (30 Oct 2009)

  30 Oct 2009; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-2.6.29.6-r6.ebuild, -clip-kernel-2.6.29.6-r5.ebuild,
