  Automatically add 'hso' to /etc/modules for 3G support.

*clip-kernel-2.6.29.6-r5 (29 Oct 2009)

  29 Oct 2009; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-2.6.29.6-r5.ebuild, -clip-kernel-2.6.29.6-r4.ebuild,
