  Fully static configurations removed. 

  02 Apr 2009; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  files/mkinitrd.clip, files/config-2.6.22.19-r10-modular,
  files/config-2.6.22.19-r10-modular-smp:
  Make CONFIG_BLK_DEV_MD a static option in modular kernels. 
  This is needed to be able to rescan RAID arrays in initrd.
  Adapt mkinitrd to be able to build support for RAID arrays
  in initrd, when the keyword RAID is present in /etc/modules.

