*clip-kernel-2.6.22.24-r6 (17 Jul 2008)

  17 Jul 2008; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-2.6.22.24-r6.ebuild, -clip-kernel-2.6.22.24-r5.ebuild,
  -files/config-2.6.22.19-r3.client, -files/config-2.6.22.19-r3.client.livecd,
  -files/config-2.6.22.19-r3.modular-smp, -files/config-2.6.22.19-r3.gtw,
  -files/config-2.6.22.19-r3.modular, -files/config-2.6.22.19-r3.gtw.livecd,
  +files/config-2.6.22.19-r4.client, +files/config-2.6.22.19-r4.client.livecd,
  +files/config-2.6.22.19-r4.modular-smp, +files/config-2.6.22.19-r4.gtw,
  +files/config-2.6.22.19-r4.modular, +files/config-2.6.22.19-r4.gtw.livecd:
  Remove GRKERNSEC_CHROOT_{MKNOD,MOUNT} from configs, since they play havoc 
  with maintainer-scripts during core update (which is run chrooted).

*clip-kernel-2.6.22.24-r5 (09 Jul 2008)

  09 Jul 2008; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-2.6.22.24-r5.ebuild, -clip-kernel-2.6.22.24-r4.ebuild:
  Bump clip-patches. Add UDP source port randomization, backported
  from 2.6.22.24.

*clip-kernel-2.6.22.24-r4 (07 Jul 2008)

  07 Jul 2008; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-2.6.22.24-r4.ebuild, -clip-kernel-2.6.22.24-r3.ebuild:
  Deny opening the kernel log buffer with CLSM_PRIV_KSYSLOG and not 
  CAP_SYS_ADMIN. Other operations (read, etc) remain possible. This 
  prevents someone starving the legitimate (launched before
  CAP_SYS_ADMIN is masked) syslog-ng's access to kmsg with a second, 
  parasitic syslog.

*clip-kernel-2.6.22.24-r3 (03 Jul 2008)

  03 Jul 2008; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-2.6.22.24-r3.ebuild, -clip-kernel-2.6.22.24-r2.ebuild,
  -files/clsm-2.6.22.24-r1.patch, +files/clsm-2.6.22.24-r2.patch:
  Fix CLSM_PRIV_IMMORTAL management, that had somehow been reverted to 
  the old version (only init can kill). Really allow ADMIN context 
  processes to kill those from any other context.

*clip-kernel-2.6.22.24-r2 (24 Jun 2008)

  24 Jun 2008; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-2.6.22.24-r2.ebuild, -clip-kernel-2.6.22.24-r1.ebuild,
  -files/clsm-2.6.22.24.patch, +files/clsm-2.6.22.24-r1.patch:
  Bump CLIP-LSM (mostly doxygen stuff - now complete).
  Bump clip-patches (misc security patches from 2.6.25 branch).

*clip-kernel-2.6.22.24 (13 May 2008)

  13 May 2008; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-2.6.22.24.ebuild, -clip-kernel-2.6.22.19-r9.ebuild:
