*clip-kernel-2.6.22.15 (14 Jan 2008)

  14 Jan 2008; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-2.6.22.15.ebuild, -clip-kernel-2.6.22.14-r2.ebuild,
  +files/8139cp.c-2.6.22.15, -files/8139cp.c-2.6.22.14:
