*clip-kernel-2.6.22.14 (04 Dec 2007)

  04 Dec 2007; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-2.6.22.14.ebuild, +files/config-2.6.22.14.modular,
  +files/config-2.6.22.14.client, +files/config-2.6.22.14.gtw,
  +files/config-2.6.22.14.modular-smp,
