  Experimental bump to 2.6.22. Configs are the same as 2.6.19.7-r18,
  except for intelfb which is removed from the client (d520) config,
  CLIP LSM is the same feature-wise as for 2.6.19.7, miscellaneous
  clip patches are the same except for a new one to make vesafb work
  without CONFIG_MODULES. 8139cp.c is basically the same, with 2.6.19 -> 2.6.22
  diffs to the original driver applied, and deprecated symbols replaced with
  their up-to-date equivalents.

