  that applies to every user, including root.

*clip-kernel-2.6.16.20 (20 Jun 2006)
  
  20 Jun 2006; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-kernel-2.6.16.20.ebuild:
  Initial import. Source tree is based on vanilla 2.6.16.20 + 
  vserver-2.0.2-rc22 + grsec-2.1.9. Config is pretty much as
  restrictive as we can go. Replaces vserver-kernel.
  Additional patches from gentoo-sources (genpatches.*-r12),
  on top of grsec_vs):
   - input.h fix for splashutils
   - fbsplash (adapted : 4200 -> 4201)
   - vesa-tng
  All needed for a nice bootsplash :)
